QUOTE OF THE DAY
=========================
"I guess we all see a little of ourselves in him. He was in
the background, and maybe we all do little great things in
the background in our own lives."
-ROGER REECE, on George Harrison. 

http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/01/obituaries/01GEOR.html?todaysheadlines


